entor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Targeted Temperature Management<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c991400 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c991400\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b748f33\" data-id=\"b748f33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e878a96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Definitions<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Therapeutic Hypothermia (TH)<\/em>: Induced Hypothermia Following Cardiac Arrest<ul><li>Older Term Now Replaced by Targeted Temperature Management<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Targeted Temperature Management (TTM)<\/em>: Strict Temperature Control Following Cardiac Arrest \u2013 Hypothermia is Not Necessarily a Required Component<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Basics<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Indication: Post-Cardiac Arrest with Return of Spontaneous Circulation (ROSC) But No Purposeful Neurologic Activity<\/li><li>Purpose: Decrease Total Body Oxygen Demand<ul><li>Improves Survival &amp; Neurologic Outcomes<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Only Absolute Contraindication: Advanced Directive or DNR Order<\/li><li>Relative Contraindications:<ul><li>Active Bleeding<\/li><li>Pregnancy<\/li><li>Severe Sepsis<\/li><li>Recent Major Surgery<\/li><li>Trauma<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Phases<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Initiation Phase<\/em><ul><li>Start as Soon as Possible After Return of Spontaneous Circulation (ROSC)<\/li><li>Goal \u2013 Reach Target Temperature Within 6 Hours<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Maintenance Phase<\/em><ul><li>Target Temperature: 32-36\u00b0C<\/li><li>Lasts for a Minimum of 24 Hours (Exact End-Point Not Clear)<\/li><li>Requires Sedation &amp; Suppression of Shivering<\/li><li>Requires Frequent Monitoring of Labs Every 4 Hours<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Rewarming<\/em><ul><li>Method: Passive or Controlled Rewarming<\/li><li>Rewarming Rates: 0.25-0.50\u00b0C\/Hour Until Normothermic<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Complications of Cooling &amp; Rewarming<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Similar to Those Seen During Accidental Hypothermia<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/accidental-hypothermia\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Accidental Hypothermia<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Surgical Critical Care: Targeted Temperature Management Targeted Temperature Management Definitions Therapeutic Hypothermia (TH): Induced Hypothermia Following Cardiac Arrest Older Term Now Replaced by Targeted Temperature Management Targeted Temperature Management (TTM): Strict Temperature Control Following Cardiac Arrest \u2013 Hypothermia is Not Necessarily a Required Component Basics Primary Indication: Post-Cardiac Arrest with Return of Spontaneous Circulation (ROSC) [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"folder":[20],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1245"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1245"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1245\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5289,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1245\/revisions\/5289"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1245"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"folder","embedda